{"about_the_game":"<u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cyborg Battles</h2></u><br>Join the battle of Novastride - where the fate of your civilization rests on your shoulders! Fight alongside your robotic comrades to emerge victorious.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/battle.gif?t=1708632782\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">High-Flying Action</h2></u><br>Engage in aerial dogfights! With heart-pumping aerial battles and stunning graphics, Novastride delivers an immersive flight experience like no other.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/dogfight.gif?t=1708632782\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rich Story</h2></u><br>Explore the sprawling cities of Novastride and uncover a rich, immersive story filled with intrigue and danger at every second!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/HQ.gif?t=1708632782\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Intense Space Experience</h2></u><br>Embark on an interstellar journey like never before, where you can explore the vast depths of space and engage in thrilling space battles! With an immersive space simulation experience, Novastride offers a range of atmospheric environments for you to explore, from rogue planets to star systems. As you navigate the stars and encounter hostile civilizations, the fate of your people hangs in the balance.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/space.gif?t=1708632782\" /><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Variety of Mechanics</h2></u><br>Seamlessly blends thrilling mechanics with immersive side quests and heart-pumping action sequences. With a vast open world to explore and endless possibilities for adventure Novastride is the ultimate space sim.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass